                <title xml:id="name260-2" xml:lang="fr-x-bhs" source="#bib260-1">Zḇīnā w-Laʿzar w-Mārūṯ w-Narsay w-ʾElīyā w-Mahrī w-Ḥabīb w-Sāḇā wa-ḇrīkīšōʿ w-Yawnān w-Šembaytēh</title>
                <title xml:id="name260-3" xml:lang="fr" source="#bib260-1">Zébinas, Lazare, Maroutha, Narsès, Élie, Mahri, Ḥabib, Saba, Berikhicho, Jonas and Chembaiteh (texte)</title>
                <title xml:id="name260-4" xml:lang="en" source="#bib260-1" syriaca-tags="#syriaca-headword">Zebinas, Lazarus, Maroutha, Narses, Elijah, Mahri, Habib, Saba, Berikhicho, Jonah and Chembaiteh (text)</title>
                <author xml:lang="fr" source="#bib260-1">Isaïe d’Arzoun</author>
                <note xml:lang="syr" type="incipit" source="#bib260-1">
                    <quote>ܒܫܢܬ ܬܡܢܥܣܪ̈ܐ ܕܡܠܟܘܬܗ ܕܫܒܘܪ ܡܠܟܐ ܕܦܪ̈ܣܝܐ: ܥܒܕ ܪܕܘܦܝܐ ܪܒܐ ܠܥܕܬܗ ܕܡܫܝܚܐ.</quote>
                </note>
                <note xml:lang="fr" type="incipit" source="#bib260-1">
                    <quote>En la dix-huitième année du règne de Shahpour roi de Perse, il fit une grande persécution contre l’Église du Christ.</quote>
                </note>
                <note xml:lang="syr" type="explicit" source="#bib260-1">
                    <quote>ܐܬܟܠܠܘ ܕܝܢ ܣܗ̈ܕܐ ܗܠܝܢ ܩܕܝ̈ܫܐ ܡܢ ܪܫܗܘܢ ܥܕܡܐ ܠܫܘܠܡܗܘܢ ܒܥܣܪܝܢ ܘܬܫܥܐ ܒܝܪܚ ܟܢܘܢ ܩܕܡ ܒܕܣܗܪܐ.</quote>
                </note>
                <note xml:lang="fr" type="explicit" source="#bib260-1">
                    <quote>Ces saints martyrs furent couronnés du premier au dernier le 29 du mois lunaire de Kanôn I.</quote>
                </note>
                <note type="editions">
                    <bibl source="#bib260-1" corresp="#bib260-6" n="1" xml:id="bib260-4">
                        <author>Bedjan, P.</author>
